Wick V4

Remastered systems, new systems, popular demands making it in and a lot of bug fixes!
Thats basically a summary of what this update is all about. It is bulky, but youll love every single part of it.

Remastered Verification

The entire concept of verification has changed. Wick will now create a channel called #verify-here that has one message with a Verify button that people could press to initiate verification.

  • Verification is now interactive and done via dms again.
  • None action: You can now make Wick not quarantine people when they join. This is super useful for servers that GIVE a role to grant access. This is also super useful for a perfect anti raid system we will get to soon. You need at least one main role in Wick before choosing this.
  • Mute action has been deprecated.
  • Verification Duration: If you have the duration set to 5m
    for an example, this is what will happen:
    • Action set to Quarantine: The duration will start once you click on Verify. Once you fail youll remain quarantined anyways.
    • Action set to Ban/Kick: The duration will start the moment you join. If you dont pass verification under 5 minutes, youll be banned/kicked
    • Action set to None: same as Quarantine. You stay without a role still if you fail.

The w!verify command deprecates the use by regular members and its
minimum permit is now 4 (trusted admins and owners). It is now used only to manually verify people.

For servers that are already using verification, Wick will delete all the verification channels, create a new channel, and send a new
embed with interactive buttons.

This is a GIF that gives a quick preview:

Press to enter Verification

What if you dont want your new members to answer captchas, but you still want the verification to help mitigate raids.

  • none as a verification mode [Press to enter]
    • No captchas involved, no dms, instant verification once the member clicks on the Verify button
    • w!v none ?set 6 to use this mode
    • If you have a main channel set in statics, Wick will try to display it to the person that passed verification in the success message so they can switch smoothly to it.
  • If the verification mode is set to none and you have premium, the joinraid will enable the captchas and dm verification once it triggers, itll later on revert back to just Press to enter once the joinraid duration has ended. This is to avoid raiders actually automating the button functionality to bypass the entire gate. PS: this is not the none you set as a verification action where Wick doesnt add the member to Quarantine on join, this none is related to the verification mode where no captcha is served but its instead an instant access to server.

Remastered Join Raid [Premium]

Joinraid has been completely remade and now, algorithms are used on top of static flags we all know. The new joinraid will not target genuine accounts and wont be blind in a sense of X joining under Ys. Itll keep a record of joins in the past X hours and will keep running every new join through all enabled algorithms. Once triggered, itll ping the warn roles and will start punishing any new join that gets flagged by the algorithms (and those that contributed to the trigger). The joinraid will always run regardless of joingate as well.
These are the Flags:

  • ID Flag: Are you aware of raid account generators? Think of this flag as the reversal. This algorithm will catch automated raids efficiently. It wont affect your server promos either!
    The concept of this specific flag can be complex, you should only bother with the Minimum Matches part.
    • Granularity: This is algorithm related, to make it simple, its the granularity in which Wick categorizes the IDs joining.
    • Minium Matches: Per each category, how many accounts are needed for the entire granular category to be considered.
    • Margin: In terms of granularity, the margin is the grace period.
  • String Flag: Do you want Wick to pay attention to the usernames of the accounts joining? Do you want it to look for specific text? Have you seen the raids where all the accounts have the same (or almost) name? This is the one for it.
    • On the dashboard, you will be able to add specific strings with some Regex-Alike special syntax operators. So you can for an example add ^fnaki and have any account joining with a name that starts with fnaki get flagged.
      • = exact match
      • ! exclude
      • ' include
      • $ ends with
  • Age Flag: You can flag any account that is young (based on your settings).
  • NoPFP Flag: You can flag any account without a profile picture.

When the join raid triggers, Wick will warn the roles you have set with the initial flags, itll lock the server when proper and will go on a rampage of bans. Normal people are not punished by this filter.
Once the joinraid is done, a full log is posted in your server with a link leading to Wicks website that displays the full list of accounts caught.

This is an image that gives a quick preview:


A lot of raiders have tested this filter, some raiders who probably raided your server at one point. Special thanks to those that were
actually open to testing the new joinraid, even though, its going to
be the one battling them officially now

Bye bye reactions: We use buttons now.

Whitelist Interaction: You can do w!whitelist OBJECT and have an interative whitelist setup.

Bot Addition Filter is now free

The joingates popular filter, Bot Addition is now entirely free for everyone. You can now only have your trusted admins, owners and people above Wick able to add bots to your server.

Unverified Bot Filter is now free

Another joingate filter is now free. You can filter out any discord bot added that hasnt been verified by Discord yet.

HEAT Anti Nuke [PREMIUM]

The heat anti nuke is finally here, its purpose is to be the fastest possible anti nuke on Discord and so, its not meant for messy servers but instead steady static servers. It uses the lockdown system plus other hidden operations that leverage Wick into detecting and ending a nuke as fast as possible with also the help of backups to always keep the server safe and clean.

  • Heat panic mode always works with the lock and unlock concept regardless of whos doing anything. Meaning that even the server owner can trigger the heat panic mode into locking and scanning. The only things safe from the heat panic mode are Immune Categories, Actions made using Wick like the mod commands, and actions made by Wick itself
  • As we know heat decreases, nukers could use this into nuking slowly in which, classic anti nuke logic is also embedded into the heat anti nuke
  • When the trigger happens and Wick is about to lock, a lot of considerations are made based on the type of the trigger, so you can notice different patterns when locking sorted by priority and situation.
  • A lot of built in logic in trying to catch malicious admins is added, things like the person that added the nuke bot, community channels spam and a lot more. Pretty much our natural instinct in a code.

Only servers that force their staff to use wick for moderation and
dont have a lot of activity going on in the domain of channels and
roles should actually consider the heat anti nuke. Only servers that have very few dangerous roles below Wick should use the heat panic mode.

Anti Vanity Change

Wick will keep an eye on any vanity change in your server and will react if someone unauthorized has been involved. The vanity is also instantly reset back to what it was to avoid vanity theft.

Giving members dangerous roles can be stopped now

You can make Wick punish someone if they give a person a dangerous role

  • Wick will not react if the person already had dangerous perms, it will still react if the person received additional* dangerous perms.
  • Immune members are safe.
  • Both the person that gave the dangerous perms and the person that received them get quarantined.

Blacklisted Words Enhancements

Wick now supports strict match and wildcards yet this cant be tested until the feature is coded into the dashboard soon. Existing added blacklisted words will be considered wildcards, Wicks own lists will be considered as strict matches.

Mute durations per every heat filter

This will be only supported via the dashboard. You can set a custom mute duration per heat filter instead of a global duration!

Threads Support

  • Wick will monitor threads the same way itd monitor regular channels.
  • Whitelist has received changes to support threads. Categories whitelist is reflected on threads (and channels obviously as well).

Auto Server Lockdown [BETA]

You can now make Wick lock all your channels if X mentions have been made under X seconds or so. This is super useful to prevent more damage caused by ping raids.

More:

  • Lockdown Changes:
    • Lockdown minimum permit is now 3, Permit 3 can lock a channel, lock all channels and post blind lock updates.
    • Lockdown now considers the main static roles you have set in Wick and will treat them the same way it treats the @everyone role. Same applies to the w!tshoot lockdown help command.
    • You can now specifically target a certain channel to lock w!lock #general or unlock w!unlock #general
    • Several bugs were fixed.
  • Purge command now accepts message links if provided instead of message Ids
  • Mod confirmations now use buttons.
  • You can choose to have Wick display Reason on AutoMute
  • w!imgclear X shortcut for w!purge X ?t images
    • iclear, imgclear, ipurge, imgp, imgpurge, ic
  • w!bcreate shortcut for w!backups take
    • bcreate, bsave, btake, createbackup
  • w!bload X shortcut for w!backups load X
    • bload, bapply, loadbackup
  • w!bdelete X shortcut for w!backups delete X
    • bdel, bdelete, deletebackup, delbackup, backupdelete
  • w!editc CASE REASON/w!editreason CASE REASON
  • w!opencase X/w!caseon X shortcut for w!cases X ?e ?on
  • w!closecase X/w!caseoff X shortcut for w!cases X ?e ?off
  • w!serverinfo shortcut for w!info -guild
    • gi, si, serverinfo, guildinfo, sinfo, ginfo
  • w!roleinfo ROLE shortcut for w!info @Role
    • ri, roleinfo, rinfo
  • w!lockc [#channel] shortcut for w!lock [#channel] ?t c
    • lockc, clock
  • w!lockchannels shortcut for w!lock ?t sc
    • lockchannels, serverlock, slock, locks, lockserver
  • w!lockupdate UPDATE shortcut for w!lock UPDATE ?t update
    • lockupdate, updatel, locku
  • More regular commands shortcuts: pre / inv / heatfilters

Bye bye rescue keys, hello Wick Authentication

You can now scan a QR Code (or copy a certain token) using your phone to basically have your ownership proof in your own phone. Just like you would use 2FA with Discord. The dashboard in the future will allow you to prove server ownership by providing the authenticator code.

Premium: the most perfect anti-raid + anti-nuke setup on Discord using Wick

Our goal with the V4 was to work on making Wick handle every size of an attack a server can face. All systems were built to function fast in super large Discord servers (which means perfection for smaller servers).

Raid Attacks

You are probably getting raided all the time, and your anti raid bots are failing (Some ratelimited by Discord, some that go offline after receiving a 200 accounts raid :) or some that are just bad but claim to be good). These raiders use a lot of accounts to force your anti raid to get ratelimited, allowing them to use the rest of the accounts to cause your server harm. Wick V4 comes with a perfect setup that renders ANY raid useless without Wick really struggling with Discord. So whats the setup?

  • 1) Join Raid
    • Wicks new join raid is super powerful (and can handle more than 40 million entries per shard which is unrealistic but very comforting). It doesnt affect your promos! and is smart. It also offers super useful filters you can use to enhance it even better.
    • All automated generated account attacks are identified with super good accuracy. We have tested using thousands and thousands of accounts.
  • 2) Verification
    • The new verification uses interactions. Its no longer automatic which means Wick wont bother until someone actually wants to verify.
    • You can make Wick not add the member to Quarantine for verification if you rely on a base role (like @Member). This means less work for Wick and more power to the join raid.
  1. Set the joinraids action to ban w!jr ban ?set 2
  2. Go over the joinraid flags and enable and tweak those you want. You can ask us in the support server if you need help.
  3. IMPORTANT:
    • Make sure your @everyone role has no global permission to view channels.
    • Your base role @Member needs to have the global permission to view channels and send messages.
    • Do not force your @Member in channels to view them, this will break your lockdown system.
    • You can deny @Member from seeing your new verification channel and also force @everyone to see the channel (but not send messages in it)
  4. Enable the joinraid w!jr 1 ?on
  5. Add your base role as a main role w!s Member ?add 5
  6. Set the verifications action to None w!v none ?set 2
  7. If you dont want Wick Captchas but just a press to enter gateway, do w!v none ?set 6. Keep in mind that Wick will start using captchas during the join raid trigger and then will resort back to instant access on press.
  8. Enable the verification w!v 1 ?on
  9. OPTIONAL: Enable Membership screening.
  10. You are prepared for 150k raids just fine :)

If you get raided, all accounts have no access to your server channels (unless they pass Wicks verification), they also cant DM your server members. All of this while Wicks joinraid is working super fast banning these raid accounts. Wicks captcha has been undetected for years now and we have backup models in store just in case. The result is a massive raid doing NOTHING but increasing your server members count temporarily.

PS: If you dont have a base role, you can still let the verification
Quarantine new accounts, but its less efficient.

Nukes

If your server has a specific set of channels or roles (your server isnt the type to create/delete/edit shit ton of channels/roles everyday) and you are forcing your staff members to moderate using Wick, you can use the fastest possible anti nuke on Discord, the heat panic mode.
The heat panic mode uses the quick lock & unlock mechanism everytime it suspects something. Once triggered, it launches a lot of operations concurrently to react and identify fast. It ends with the backups system synchronizing the latest backup taken with your current servers state removing any damage done.

  1. Enable the antinuke w!an 1 ?on
  2. Enable the backups system w!an 3a ?on
  3. Enable the panic mode w!anp 1 ?on
  4. If you have a tickets bot, add the tickets category to the Immune Categories using w!anp CATEGORY-ID ?add 6
  5. Tweak the heat to your liking using the w!anc command
  6. Enable the heat algorithm w!anp 2 ?on
